my account seems to be reported by a group of still-Trump-supporters who also full of nationalism, meanwhile i am a strongly Biden advocate since his presidential election and more far from his vice-president time, maybe it was me that ever claimed i loved Biden very much in chinese then i was attacked by them, i also found that there were something strange on my account which made me feel they once stole my account to do something violating twitter rules, please unlock my account for me dear twitter, i can't stand what the Trump's suppoters achieved what they wanted harassing me.

My account has been abusively reported by advocators against freedom of speech, who posted hateful content for no good reason. I believe my rebuttal against their speech is what had provoked them towards abusing twitter mechanics to report certain contents I reported which, despite by looking not immediately relevant to the hashtags I posted, are in fact used as community hashtags from which we organise social events and exchange opinions. Since Twitter has not imposed regulations in protection of the use of such hashtags, malevolent parties, since they find themselves offended by freedom of speech, abused this lack of protection to attack me, for which I find very upsetting. I believe Twitter is a just advocator for freedom of speech and will help those underprivileged by providing them with a space where their voice can be heard, an advocator that does good, not evil.
